&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1W810wwWXU8Q7kNvgEhxWK5&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBexJo8JVNzgWUgpZLYQ46PFTzRZ264DjBMcT1KAtcdvg&oe=671E18CB"}, {"file_name": "immagine-2021-12-07-160621.png", "id": "1097588264148206", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031600_1097588267481539_1441771463292176882_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nML3lVMvW4EQ7kNvgEOpH3O&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBeMdtCLVppqP6tpmt_dD7gywkCdBpRKllrVddcR3QUhg&oe=671E283E"}, {"file_name": "screenshot-bully2 (1).png", "id": "3109815769292844", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982563_3109815772626177_6284524619823654227_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rt1220cJ3-cQ7kNvgGKAfxq&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAbQHhq-w4GCYl4lXQTRusF5GH3Q9LDMVCLbajkQAnbWw&oe=671E2C1A"}, {"file_name": "screenshot-bully3.png", "id": "732978577649854", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982492_732978580983187_8954213730478558859_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZSNw43hvYvAQ7kNvgGgOKKl&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCpoliOjd20b5iDROnPTzuPlIvwbue6sdGjzqBTQeSEww&oe=671E3A44"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Ultrasclash V", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Ultrasclash V is a unique blend of three of the most beloved gaming concepts: anime, fighting, and sandbox approach. Combined, they create a fast paced, high octane virtual reality experience, in which you fight hordes of hostile cacti-men in a desperate, yet unmistakably hilarious, fight for survival.\n\nFEATURES\n\nPunch Movement System: we created a VR locomotion system which allows you to roam the map using your fists, punching in the direction you choose to move to!\n\nCrazy Bullet Time fights: just like in The Matrix, freeze time to gain a tactical advantage and defeat your opponents.\n\nPhysical engine: 